# ğŸ›’ Simple E-Commerce API

This is a basic e-commerce API built with Flask, Flask-SQLAlchemy, and MySQL. It manages Users (Customers), Orders, and Products.

---

## ğŸ”§ Tech Used

* Python
* Flask
* MySQL

---

## ğŸ“Œ Endpoints

### Users (Customers)

* `GET /customers` â€“ Get all users
* `GET /customers/<id>` â€“ Get one user
* `POST /customers` â€“ Create a user
* `PUT /customers/<id>` â€“ Update a user
* `DELETE /customers/<id>` â€“ Delete a user

### Products

* `GET /products` â€“ Get all products
* `GET /products/<id>` â€“ Get one product
* `POST /products` â€“ Create a product
* `PUT /products/<id>` â€“ Update a product
* `DELETE /products/<id>` â€“ Delete a product

### Orders

* `POST /orders` â€“ Create an order
* `PUT /orders/<order_id>/add_product/<product_id>` â€“ Add product to order
* `DELETE /orders/<order_id>/remove_product/<product_id>` â€“ Remove product from order
* `GET /orders/user/<user_id>` â€“ All orders for a user
* `GET /orders/<order_id>/products` â€“ All products in an order

---

## ğŸ—ƒ Relationships

* One user â†’ many orders
* Orders â†” products (many-to-many)

